English: Representing Magentos highest level of partner engagement, Magento Platinum Partners have established themselves as leaders and innovators of key products and services designed to help merchants and brands grow their business. Magento reserves the Platinum level for select trusted partners that are committed to offering integrations of commerce features, functions, and tools, as well as back-end systems and operations, to extend and enhance the power of the Magento commerce platform.
